# Google Sign-In (Google Identity Services)
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Create a project (or pick one you already have)
# 3. "Create Credentials" -> "OAuth client ID" -> Application type: "Web application"
# 4. Under "Authorized JavaScript origins" add: http://localhost:5173
#    (add your production domain too once you deploy)
# 5. Copy the generated Client ID and paste it below
# 6. Copy this file to .env.local and restart `npm run dev`
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
